The Gist of the App:

App Names:
1. One Food Only
2. Recipe+
3. CookAny
4. OneDish
5. RecipeHub

The app shares all recipes that involve certain ingredients and are rated based on difficulty and time-consumption. For example, if a person inputs "Potato",
the app should show all recipes involving a potato. Recipes will also contain parameters like: Difficulty, average cooking time, number of recipes, calorie count,
nutritional value, best-eaten in ___.